# This directory is the Vercel static output root (see vercel.json).
#
# It is intentionally (almost) empty. Only files placed here are web-served as
# static assets. The serverless functions in `api/` deploy and run regardless
# of this setting. Pointing `outputDirectory` here — instead of the repo root
# (`.`) — stops source files like `db/schema.sql`, `lib/auth.js`, and
# `package.json` from being fetchable at predictable URLs.
#
# Do not move secrets or source into this folder.
